OL,5, Baroness Morrissey has said an apology 
OL,6, by the CBI for failing to fire people  
OL,7, who sexually harassed female colleagues
OL,8, is "too little, too late".             
OL,10,FThe diversity campaigner and financier 
OL,11,Fsaid she felt the lobby giant was      
OL,12,Ffinished and criticised firms who have 
OL,13,Fyet to publicly cut ties with the CBI. 
OL,15,FThe CBI apologised following a report  
OL,16,Ffrom an independent law firm into      
OL,17,Fmisconduct allegations including rape. 
OL,19,FIt admitted it had hired "toxic" staff 
OL,20,Fand failed to fire "offenders".        
